===Etymology===
{{F.}}, believed to be named after the village of Chardonnay in the [[w:Mâconnais|Mâconnais]] region of France, where [[w:Pouilly-Fuissé|Pouilly-Fuissé]] is currently produced; it is possible that the variety was first bred there

